snippet.title: Operation: Inner Space - Classic and unique Windows 3.1 game
snippet.description:
I loved this one when I was a kid, it's a pretty unique and addictive game combining several genres or if you will, several mini-games.

You get to pick your ship, upgrade it, do space races, space dogfight, build alliances, and probably more.
